Symfony - base64 file upload API
------------
Base64 file upload API built with Symfony v5.1.


Local setup
---------------
```bash
$ git clone https://github.com/kristijansoldo/symfony-base64-fileupload.git
$ cd symfony-base64-fileupload
$ composer install
$ symfony server:start
```

Upload file
---------------
```
POST /file/upload HTTP/1.1
Host: 127.0.0.1:8000
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"file": "data:image/jpeg;base64,"
}
```
